sec.p:
The regional emissions of IMAGE model were downscaled at the level of countries and a 0.5 × 0.5 grid using the downscaling method that has been described by Van Vuuren et al. (2007b). This method is basically organized around the so-called Kaya-identity (Kaya 1989):
